  "text": "contours, the spectra of out-of-plane membrane fluctuations were calculated. Fits of a theoretical description of these fluctuation spectra to the measured data resulted in values for the bending rigidity κ and surface tension σ of the vesicles in the absence or presence of 1 μM GS. Details about the procedure can be found in [CITATION_1] .",
